WHAT PROBLEM IT SOLVES
Models the Arrow Lake disaggregated tile architecture, hybrid CPU core
cluster, and NPU as formulas, enabling accurate prediction of AI grading
latency, encoding throughput, and thermal behaviour on Intel mobile
platforms.

